subject:

TAKE TIME TO LEARN MORE ABOUT GOD

===================================================================
verse:

How great is our Lord! His power is absolute! His
comprehension is beyond understanding! (Ps. 147:5)

===================================================================
reflection:

Sometimes we feel as if we don’t understand ourselves— what
we want, how we feel, what’s wrong with us, or what we
should do about it. But God’s understanding has no limit,
and therefore He understands us fully. If you feel troubled
and don’t understand yourself, remember that God understands
you perfectly. So take your mind off yourself and focus on
God.

===================================================================
prayer:

Lord God, Your understanding of us is limitless, for You
know every thought, every feeling, and every moment of our
lives (Psalm 139). When we feel confused or troubled, remind
us that You see us fully and love us deeply. Help us to
focus not on our doubts or fears but on Your perfect
knowledge and care, trusting in Your guiding hand. May Your
peace calm our hearts as we rest in Your unending wisdom and
grace. Amen. (AI)

===================================================================
